br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z6xFaVvzkzY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ6xFaVvzkzY&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c0d1faea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z6xFaVvzkzY</a><br />\nม็อบ 18 ตุลา 63 - เริ่มแล้ว<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0g1jzbYqk1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0g1jzbYqk1A&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=59b3dc5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0g1jzbYqk1A</a><br />\n🔴: #ม็อบ18ตุลา อนุสาวรีย์ชัยฯ"},{"pid":"a302ed525dc341982fd79c69bfecd5fa54e9a019","tid":2248274,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0dSV7cpv5Bs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0dSV7cpv5Bs&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=e47ecc7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0dSV7cpv5Bs</a><br />\nLIVE! บรรยากาศการชุมนุมแยกอโศก #ม็อบ18ตุลา"},{"pid":"8e33c064f95059cf6ce2a7eab233f9389f43d67a","tid":2248274,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶茶聯盟"},{"pid":"46138b0616904b37c136da7af8f4f95de5b0fb66","tid":2248274,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e33c064f95059cf6ce2a7eab233f9389f43d67a","tid":2248274,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶茶聯盟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.bld.news/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/qjv7vddhncg5fz72biy4vbobe4-600x400-2-e1587058860107-700x366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bld.news%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Fqjv7vddhncg5fz72biy4vbobe4-600x400-2-e1587058860107-700x366.jpg&h=fe9d01ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681354c04eeedcd9f2d41e062472665a11006387","tid":2248274,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"反極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca253a1c9a2e936628deace76873114bd1262692","tid":2248274,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681354c04eeedcd9f2d41e062472665a11006387","tid":2248274,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"反極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d3dac6de84dccc4e3fa41ef8f8249e988f14d8","tid":2248274,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"發動民主支持泰國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c0c7c8061177c811ba55826c5a93c4314653d3","tid":2248274,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">在台泰生組聯盟 籲釋放反政府示威者</span></strong><br />\n林曉慧 張梓嘉 / 台北報導  2020-10-18 19:10 最後更新：2020-10-18 20:15<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2Xd8Grur-HU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2Xd8Grur-HU&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=d695a4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2Xd8Grur-HU</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國7月中旬後爆發2014年軍事政變以來，最大規模反政府示威。16日警方首度以強力水柱，以及噴灑具有催淚效果的物質，驅趕和平集會民眾並進行逮捕。<span class=\"red\">一群在台灣唸書的泰國學生，組成「台灣推動泰國民主聯盟」，下午在泰國駐台經濟文化辦公室一旁集會，譴責清場行為，呼籲儘快釋放遭逮捕民眾。</span><br />\n<br />\n邊集會邊看書的大學生，身旁標語被突然到來的警察撕毀，下一刻，從頭到腳被淋上藍漆，卻無抵抗餘地。在北藝大唸書的泰國學生那琪和夥伴們透過行動劇，呈現16日那天在曼谷示威的民眾和學生如何被對待。<br />\n<br />\n台灣推動泰國民主聯盟發言人那琪表示，「就像以我來說，我在台灣，但我的心完全和抗爭的人連結，為什麼他們會在那邊？，我能想像他們的處境，我能想像他們的心境。」<br />\n<br />\n警方以強力水柱，以及噴灑具有催淚作用的物質驅趕，民眾只要被噴到藍色的水，就等於被標記參與抗爭。那琪說，有不少大學生被逮捕，雖然自己的朋友目前安全，卻為泰國的民主與未來感到憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n台灣推動泰國民主聯盟發言人那琪認為，「說是民主政府民主國家，他們卻用武力去阻止人民表達自己的想法。」<br />\n<br />\n台師大泰國學生貝斯則說：「他們以前就想要到大學裡面去抗議，那些大學那些學校被政府，政府就是說不能開給他們辦活動。」<br />\n<br />\n近30位在台的泰國學生參加集會，有人比出三指手勢，象徵反抗獨裁政府。還有超過20位台灣民眾到場聲援，有標語寫道台灣相挺泰國，標記是泰港台網友串聯的奶茶聯盟。台灣推動泰國民主聯盟希望這次活動反映到泰國政府，聽取人民訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.pts.org.tw/article/497466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pts.org.tw%2Farticle%2F497466&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=f17b756f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.pts.org.tw/article/497466</a>"},{"pid":"8d8eaa4524241e1f781a6c99974ae4d31727d593","tid":2248274,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18d3dac6de84dccc4e3fa41ef8f8249e988f14d8","tid":2248274,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"發動民主支持泰國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/15/phpKEe6BZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F15%2FphpKEe6BZ.jpg&h=252c0b11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bac0e316fc3e9f4c15693e03214c0b9bd317949","tid":2248274,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/shujamtaro/status/1316489695803699205?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshujamtaro%2Fstatus%2F1316489695803699205%3Fs%3D21&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c2f1dd4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshujamtaro%2Fstatus%2F1316489695803699205%3Fs%3D21&h=dcab2c5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/shujamtaro/status/1316489695803699205?s=21</a>"}]}